extends layout

block content
  h1 Volume Arc Meter
  p Audio API volume: <span id="apiVol"></span>
  p.
    Arbitrary Volume number: <span id="vol">0</span>
    <span class="calc">API volume * 1000 (rounded up)</span>

  span#begin.button Click here to begin

  p#countdown 0

  canvas#meter(width="300", height="300") Sorry your browser does not support HTML5 canvas

  span#stop.button Stop
  a#save.button(href="#") Save Audio